snippet.title: LASER TAG MASSACRE - 80's Slasher Game - Trailer
snippet.description:
ADD TO COLLECTION: https://liminalroad.itch.io/lasertag-massacre
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/p3tyrDKC3X

Halloween night turns deadly when five friends decide to throw a party in an abandoned arcade deep in rural Campinas, Brazil. What was meant to be just a game turns into their worst nightmare, proving that sometimes, play time can be deadly.

RELEASE 12.20.2024
